<p>We collect the following types of data when you use our services:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information</strong>: Name, email, phone number, and address.</li>
    <li><strong>Account Information</strong>: Username, password, and rental history.</li>
    <li><strong>Payment Information</strong>: Billing details (if applicable).</li>
